    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nThey were surprised __ hear the news of the merger so suddenly.\n A) to hearing\n B) on hearing\n C) to hear\n D) No improvement\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\n\"To hear\" is correct as it shows the correct infinitive form after \"surprised.\"",
